        "content": "### All Healthy?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ ($json.statusCode || 200) < 400 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Uptime Metric · ②→ Already Alerted? (State Check)",
